sequenceDiagram
    actor Pengguna
    participant Halaman as Halaman Login
    participant Controller as AuthController
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Pengguna->>Halaman: Input email dan password
    Halaman->>Controller: POST /login
    Controller->>DB: SELECT user WHERE email
    DB-->>Controller: Data user
    
    alt Password benar
        Controller->>Controller: Generate JWT
        Controller-->>Halaman: Token berhasil
        Halaman-->>Pengguna: Redirect ke Dashboard
    else Password salah
        Controller-->>Halaman: 401 Unauthorized
        Halaman-->>Pengguna: Tampilkan error
    end
